    {
      "id": "1b34750c-f3ba-80e8-b330-f824f69b85a0",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors look to address these issues by proposing and Enhanced vector recommender that automatically adjusts the learner’s interests, requirements and knowledge level. The improved preprocessing is subject to Content Based Filtering recommenders in order to deliver the actual recommendations. These recommendations are sub-sequently ranked using a collaborative filtering approach. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1b34750c-f3ba-80e8-b330-f824f69b85a0",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
